title: SockGuy, Rocket Man, Classic Sock, Sporty and Stylish, 3 Inches - Small/Medium
features: CLASSIC SOCK - Our most popular Classic socks feature off-beat, original designs that appeal to a broad range of athletes, from professionals to weekend warriors to multi-sport enthusiasts who like to have unique socks to match their personality and attitude.

SPORTY AND STYLISH - Put a pair on today and your feet will be happy and look fantastic! Like our entire line of performance socks, all of our crew socks are purpose-built and functionally fashionable. We also feature a double stitched heel & toe for added strength and durability.
COMFORTABLE - Our socks features superior softness and comfort to help eliminate blisters and hot spots.
PERFECT FIT - "Stretch-to-Fit" sizing system and our exclusive "Easy-fit" cuff for a perfect fit every time on any foot.
PRODUCT MATERIALS - 75% moisture wicking micro denier acrylic, 15% nylon, 10% spandex. Mesh upper above your foot allows maximum ventilation and breathability.
